minimal support for GNU builtin _Float## types, 2024-01-17, v0.6.3~1^2)
to support conversions needed by `<math.h>` in C and `<cmath>` in C++.

Pull-request: #252

castxml: Add minimal support for GNU builtin _Float## types

gcc >= 7 support these in C.  g++ >= 13 support these in C++.
LLVM/Clang does not implement them, so simulate them.

Fixes: #251
Output: Generalize output logic for simulated builtin types
test: Clarify names of __float128 tests
